ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectDESIGNATED BARLEY - 2008-2009 UNSOLD STOCK ** Transfer to 2009-2010 Pool **
PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to transfer the DESIGNATED BARLEY unsold from the preceding pool, that began on August 1, 2008 and ended on July 31, 2009 to the current pool period, that began August 1, 2009 and will end July 31, 2010.
